Products.description: The Zion Williamson 2019-20 Panini Prizm Rookie is the poster card for the hobby's resurgance during the 2019-20 NBA season. Similar to the base Prizm rookies of Ja Morant, Luka Doncic, Trae Young, and Jayson Tatum, Panini printed a plentiful amount of this one card. Only time will tell if this affects demand in the long haul, but if Zion lives up to the sky high expectations and claims the NBA's throne then watch out. Drafted #1 overall out of Duke University in the 2019 NBA Draft, Zion is easily the most explosive, talented, and dominant prospect to come out of college basketball within the last decade. His highlight dunks throw fans and the media into a frenzy, with many comparing Zion to a young LeBron James - should he be able to live up to the hype, this card will become a must-have staple in any collection.
